com.kuka.jogging.provider

Interface IJoggingSupport

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ICartesianJoggingSupport, IJointJoggingSupport

    public interface IJoggingSupport
    Interface which enables the implementing class to set a timeout for jogging motions.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void setTimeout(long timeout)
      Timeout for jogging movement.

    • Method Detail

      • setTimeout

        void setTimeout(long timeout)
        Timeout for jogging movement. If no new jogging command arrives within the timeout the motion stops. Zero timeout results in no stopping of the device.
        Parameters:
        timeout - for jogging in ms.
